  expReward: 1000
  offerDialogue:
    name: Professor Bhan
    sentences:
    - Build a safe crossing for the merchant cart using your basic wooden beams.
      Make sure to brace your structure with triangles!
    - The storm washed out the crossing over Muddy Creek. We need to get a supply
      cart to the other side
    - You have a budget of $10000. Head over to the Drafting Table when you are ready
      to build.
  reminderDialogue:
    name: Professor Bhan
    sentences:
    - What are you waiting for? The creek isn't going to bridge itself!
    - Tap the Drafting Table to get started. Build across the gap and run the simulation.
  finishedContractDialogue:
    name: Professor Bhan
    sentences:
    - wqewqe
